title: Indonesia : number of internet users 2017 to 2023
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of users in millions, containing a total of 7 data points.
In general Number of users in millions has rose over the Year.
Number of users in millions is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2021, and lastly roughly constant from 2021 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2019 and 2020.
The highest Number of users in millions, of value 149.9 was reached at Year 2023
Minimum Number of users in millions about 84.0 was reached at Year 2017
